# Hybrid from-source ESP-IDF build artifacts (created by custom_sdkconfig).
# All machine-generated by pioarduino's Arduino-as-component build and must
# never be committed: ~3700 files of fetched IDF components, the lib-builder
# scratch dir, and the generated sdkconfig files.
managed_components/
.dummy/
sdkconfig.defaults
sdkconfig.*
dependencies.lock
